headline: Berkshire Boosts Mitsubishi Stake, Increases Investment in Japan
summary: Berkshire lifts its Mitsubishi stake to 10.23%, deepening its Japan bet with rising dividends, low-cost debt and governance gains.

headline: Raymond James Names New ETF Head as it Prepares to Launch First Funds
